<div class='col-sm-12'>
  <h4>{{t "Speak Mode" key="speak_mode"}}</h4>
</div>
<div class='col-sm-12'>
  <img src={{path "images/speak-mode.png"}} alt="" style='width: 100%;' >
</div>
<div class='col-sm-12' style="margin-top: 16px;">
  <ul class="usage-checklist">
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Speak Mode is where communication happens. Tap buttons to build sentences in the message bar, then tap the bar to speak them aloud." key="speak_mode_1"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "The left panel gives you quick access to navigation, phrase building, session logs, goals, and settings — all without leaving the board." key="extra_speak_mode_left_panel"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "The right panel shows board details, color key, and contextual tools to help you stay oriented as you navigate between boards." key="extra_speak_mode_right_panel"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Both panels can be hidden for a distraction-free experience — just tap the expand button or collapse the header to maximize board space." key="extra_speak_mode_hide_panels"}}</li>
  </ul>
</div>
